cc:Work.dc:description:
A frame for an engraving ; can be either standing or hanging, both in portrait or landscape
This box is a frame for an engraving.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes EngravingFrame Command line short: boxes EngravingFrame
